name: British Airways First Class Flight, Boeing 747, San Francisco to London Heathrow
description:
Fancy being a Patron? https://www.patreon.com/paulstripreports

On this flight, join me in seat 1A on an overnight First Class trip between San Francisco and London Heathrow. The video features all the ground and inflight services, all phases of the flight, the food, and a special A-List celebrity cameo!

Enjoy, and please leave me a comment if you liked it!
